SUMMARY:Deadline: Sarabande Foundation: Studio Residency 2026/27 (UK-based 
 only)
DESCRIPTION:The Sarabande Foundation\, founded by Lee Alexander McQueen\, o
 ffers subsidised London studio residencies for creatives across discipline
 s (fine art\, fashion\, design\, digital)\, with structured mentoring and 
 pro bono expert support. ELIGIBILITY: applicants must have a UK address an
 d the right to work in the UK\; the foundation cannot sponsor visas. Deadl
 ine 1 August 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Sarabande Foundation\nLocation: London
 \, United Kingdom. Requires a UK address and right to work in the UK\; no 
 visa sponsorship.\nAward: Heavily subsidised studio space (GBP 1 per sq ft
  per month including utilities)\, mentoring from industry experts\, pro bo
 no business support\, and access to the Sarabande network. Free to apply.\
 nDuration: Residencies start November 2026.\n\nMore: https://sarabandefoun
 dation.org/en-us/pages/studio-residencies-scholarships?utm_source=artifici
 alnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://sarabandefoundation.org/en-us/pages/studio-residencies-scholars
 hips?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:London\, United Kingdom. Requires a UK address and right to work i
 n the UK\; no visa sponsorship.
END:VEVENT
